  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I walked all night and arrived in the morning in Perpignan, rather outside Perpignan.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just as it became light, I said to myself, oh, I must go and just have a little bit of sleep.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was in the forest, and I slept an hour or two.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went into town, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I didn't really know what I would do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How-- if I tell the French I'm here, they arrest me again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So on the square, I saw a group of Boy Scouts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember I used to be a Boy Scout in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went to one of them, and I gave him the greeting, Boy Scout greeting, like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, he returned it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this one fellow who looked sympathetic, and I told him, look, I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I run away from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm a-- a refugee from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And somehow or other, I have to go and get to my cousins in Limoges.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my French was very bad at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he took me-- took to his home, introduced me to his parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the parents gave me coffee and breakfast and-- and treated me wonderful, gave me some money, gave me a ticket to go-- train ticket-- to go to Limoges.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was really tremendous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wish I remember the name of the people, but slip my mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Limoges, I went to the address that I knew that my cousins lived there, that they-- they-- house to themselves with a garden, and-- and-- and they were very happy to receive me.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I slept in the same room with [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maxwell, ?] with the youngest.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
